list.name: Default
list.comment: Added button for saving the entire state of the program. Still not implemented yet.

task.summary: Default task

Text works with undo/redo (one character at a time) Currently fixing bug that causes everything to be bubble text.
Comment out 459-462 of this commit in order to avoid the bug and always have it be bubble text.
Backspace calls undo if you are writing in a text box and deletes the last character that was written, if there is one to delete.
just some deleted TODOs. commit in order to pull
Undo and redo stack now hold a list of shapeDef's instead of just one.
Backspace does not cause bubble text anymore.
undo works on entire words. Must click a color before pressing undo. Some bugs with it are still there.
Fixed conflicts from recent pull.
Added in the ability to condense strings from entire actions by doing an undo/redo.
undid recent pull. no real changes.

Merge should work now. Copied previous changes and then added mine in.
Weird bug where if you make a text box and then resize the window, and then click in the window again, it continues the text where you left off.
Text Color and Text Size can now be modified by the ControllerBox
Toggle clickable option added. Lets user click through window when clickable is false. Does not currently work if trying to click on the home page window.

Moved code to remove all handlers into a method in order to remove handlers before starting a new type of event.
Touch capability for send to back should work. Still not tested.
Eraser is working.
Erase Transparent is working.
Removed the option for Erase White.
Refactored some code.
More Code Refactoring.
Fixed bug where circles would be created if you pressed make circles, then toggle clickable twice.
Controllerbox automatically becomes smaller when not being hovered over. Becomes bigger again when being hovered over. Does not currently work very well when not clickable.

Potentially fixes save image on ubuntu based on https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4373288/how-can-i-construct-java-robot-class-methods-into-a-method-of-my-own-making. If it does not, then does not introduce and new issues. Also added in some new comments.
Redo stack clears on events that are not undo/redo.
Added in a color picker so that any color may be picked by the user.
Fixed bug where drawing on other nodes can sometimes lead to nodes not being deleted when desired.
Circles are now made as annuli. (Ring shaped objects.)
Fixed bug where circles get completely erased whenever the eraser is used.
Arrow drawer now adds straight lines.
Arrow drawer now adds straight arrows.
some added comments
Easier to see box as it gets created.
Removed decoration from the mouse catching window. This fixed the bug where drawings were offset.
Added in some items for the new stack.

undoStack changed so that it now holds ChangeItems in preparation for adding more features. Change items are any kind of change that may be done. So far have implemented one that adds shapes, and one for erasing certain areas.
The class MoveShape has been created, but it has not been implemented.
The ChangeItems edit the stack based on what kind of change they need to bring about.
Changed the name of the method commitShape to commitChange.
Started making a separate controller box in javafx that has icons.

added various buttons to the IconControllerBox. I also added in methods to snap the controllerbox to the left, right, and top of a given drawing stage.
Most images equivalent to Ardesia images.
Changed style of size changer to UTILITY.
fixed bug where circles and arrows got painted underneath of other things until another circle or arrow was drawn.
Added in method setIconSizes which goes through the icons and sets the size of the button.
Added in button to set the buttons' sizes. Moved TODO list to google drive and to issues on github.
Added some of the png files to git.
Solves issue where user could not draw over toggle clickable area without being unable to later toggle clickable back on.
Fixes some of the issues where the drawings would appear over top of the controllerbox rendering it impossible to click.
Now shows a pencil as the cursor.
Now shows various different images as cursor based on what is being done.
Fixed bug where the picturestage would show itself on top of the mousecatching stage when a size is picked. Made some small name changes.
Fixed bug where dialog would pop up below the drawing area.
Fix issue where controllerbox dialog would show up under stage. also makes sure it stays on the screen.
Fixes issue where the controllerbox would end up below the other two stages
Added button for saving the entire state of the program. Still not implemented yet.
